WEBVTT

00:04:29.207 --> 00:04:31.520
RL: Ne, ne slažem se s tim.

00:04:31.520 --> 00:04:35.257
Mislim da -

00:04:35.257 --> 00:04:37.392
izvinite, čujem eho

00:04:37.392 --> 00:04:40.949
kroz mikrofon -

00:04:40.949 --> 00:04:45.776
njegovi postupci nisu bili primereni

00:04:45.776 --> 00:04:50.551
jer je ugrozio živote ljudi,

00:04:50.551 --> 00:04:52.023
na duge staze,

00:04:52.023 --> 00:04:54.177
i znam da u javnosti,

00:04:54.177 --> 00:04:58.251
gospodin Snouden i neki novinari govore

00:04:58.251 --> 00:05:01.681
da stvari koje je razotkrio